* phase-6: control sections (USE/BLOCK).  Code goes in the blank section 0;
* BLOCK opens a labeled-common section COMM, and the `,0` overrides its type to
* a write-access data control section (0).  VAL lands in COMM at its own offset
* 0; LDA VAL relocates against section COMM, while TRA START stays a section-0
* relocation.
       OUNAME SECTEST
START  LDA   VAL
       TRA   START
       BLOCK COMM,0
VAL    OCT   123
       END   START
